# clark-stealth-chromium patch #49 - coherent WebGPU GPUAdapterInfo.
#
# Source: chromium 148.0.7778.96
#   third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgpu/gpu_adapter.cc
#
# WebGPU exposes adapter identity through GPUAdapter.info and
# GPUDevice.adapterInfo. If WebGL is spoofed to a seed/profile GPU but WebGPU
# reports the host adapter, detectors get a clean cross-API mismatch. This patch
# maps WebGPU vendor/architecture/device/description to the same seed-selected
# GPU pool used by the WebGL patch, and respects explicit
# --fingerprint-gpu-{vendor,renderer} overrides.
